fehd.ADR_EN: G/F., NO. 62 HOLLYWOOD ROAD, CENTRAL, HONG KONG
fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環荷李活道62號地下

result.adr_address: 62 Hollywood Rd, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: La Cabane Wine Bistro

reviews.text: Love this little wine bistro! Very quaint place and service is good too. They have an amazing wine menu with lots of organic wines and at rather reasonable prices. Will make this my usual stop whenever I'm in HK.

I heard the staff import wines& ingredients from France. Also they are very friendly.
I tried one wine and creamy cheese. It’s very nice!!
This is a place where you can enjoy great natural wines with reasonable prices.

Wonderful bijou wine bar if you are hunting down biodynamic and organic small production wines served up with home-made pates, unusual cheeses and cured meats, fabulous sardine amuse-gueule tapas style dishes. Decor is mediaeval Barcelona old quarter meets southern France country rustic. Appreciative crowd and friendly French management. Gets busy early!
Great food, great wine and super chill vibe !
